%% Multi-agent routing via LangGraph
graph TD
    Q[User request] --> R{Router - LangGraph}
    R --> SQL[SQL Agent]
    R --> SPARK[PySpark Agent]
    R --> ETL[ETL Agent]
    R --> DQ[Data Quality Agent]
    R --> DOC[Documentation Agent]
    R --> AIR[Airflow Agent]
    R --> DBT[dbt Agent]
    R --> RAGA[RAG Agent]

    RAGA -->|context| SQL
    RAGA -->|context| SPARK
    RAGA -->|context| ETL

    SQL --> OUT[Grounded, validated response]
    SPARK --> OUT
    ETL --> OUT
    DQ --> OUT
    DOC --> OUT
    AIR --> OUT
    DBT --> OUT
